### ============================================================
### 第19次课 — Spring统一异常处理 + 未覆盖接口测试
### 使用前：
###   1. 先执行"用户注册"获取user1_token和user2_token
###   2. 替换下方 token 变量值为实际JWT
### ============================================================

@base = http://localhost:8080
@token = your-jwt-token-here
@token2 = another-user-jwt-token-here

### ############################################################
### 一、Token 获取（先执行）
### ############################################################

### 注册用户1（测试主体）
POST {{base}}/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "exception_test",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "13800000001",
  "email": "test1@example.com"
}

### 登录用户1 → 获取 token，替换上方 @token
POST {{base}}/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "exception_test",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 注册用户2（用于越权测试）
POST {{base}}/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "exception_test2",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "13800000002",
  "email": "test2@example.com"
}

### 登录用户2 → 获取 token2，替换上方 @token2
POST {{base}}/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "exception_test2",
  "password": "123456"
}

### ############################################################
### 二、异常处理 — HTTP 状态码验证（第19次课重点）
### ############################################################

### ==================== 400 BadRequestException ====================

### [400] 购物车为空时创建订单
POST {{base}}/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "张三",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### ==================== 400 参数校验失败 ====================

### [400] 创建订单 — 收货人为空
POST {{base}}/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### [400] 创建订单 — 电话格式错误
POST {{base}}/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "张三",
  "telephone": "abc",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### [400] 添加购物车 — productId为null
POST {{base}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": null,
  "quantity": 1
}

### [400] 添加购物车 — quantity为0
POST {{base}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 0
}

### [400] 添加购物车 — quantity为负数
POST {{base}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": -5
}

### [400] 修改购物车 — 缺少newQuantity
PUT {{base}}/cart/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
}

### [400] 修改勾选状态 — selected超出范围
PUT {{base}}/cart/1/selected
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "selected": 3
}

### ==================== 403 ForbiddenException ====================

### [403] 越权查看他人订单 — 先创建订单，记下order_id，再用token2访问
GET {{base}}/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### [403] 越权操作他人购物车 — 修改数量
PUT {{base}}/cart/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

{
  "newQuantity": 5
}

### [403] 越权删除他人购物车项
DELETE {{base}}/cart/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### ==================== 404 ResourceNotFoundException ====================

### [404] 查询不存在的订单
GET {{base}}/orders/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### [404] 访问不存在的购物车项
PUT {{base}}/cart/99999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "newQuantity": 1
}

### [404] 删除不存在的购物车项
DELETE {{base}}/cart/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== 500 RuntimeException（未改造服务抛的） ====================

### [500] 注册 — 用户名已存在（UserServiceImpl未改造，仍抛RuntimeException）
POST {{base}}/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "exception_test",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "13811111111",
  "email": "dup@example.com"
}

### ############################################################
### 三、Cart：之前未覆盖的边界场景
### ############################################################

### ==================== 准备：添加测试数据 ====================

### 添加商品到购物车（用于后续测试）
POST {{base}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 添加第二个商品
POST {{base}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": 3,
  "quantity": 1
}

### ==================== GET /cart — 边界场景 ====================

### 正常查询购物车列表
GET {{base}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 未登录查询购物车（应返回401或拦截器错误）
GET {{base}}/cart

### Token格式错误
GET {{base}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token-here

### ==================== POST /cart — 边界场景 ====================

### 添加不存在的商品
POST {{base}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": 99999,
  "quantity": 1
}

### 超过库存数量添加
POST {{base}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 99999
}

### productId为0
POST {{base}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": 0,
  "quantity": 1
}

### productId为负数
POST {{base}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": -1,
  "quantity": 1
}

### ==================== PUT /cart/{cart_id} — 边界场景 ====================

### newQuantity为负数
PUT {{base}}/cart/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "newQuantity": -1
}

### newQuantity为0
PUT {{base}}/cart/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "newQuantity": 0
}

### cart_id为非数字
GET {{base}}/cart/abc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== PUT /cart/{cart_id}/selected — 边界场景 ====================

### selected为null
PUT {{base}}/cart/1/selected
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
}

### ==================== DELETE /cart/selected — 边界场景 ====================

### 空购物车批量删除（无勾选商品）
DELETE {{base}}/cart/selected
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== 全链路：添加→勾选→统计 → 下单 ====================

### 全选购物车
PUT {{base}}/cart/selected/batch
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "selected": 1
}

### 查看已勾选数量
GET {{base}}/cart/selected/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 查看总数量
GET {{base}}/cart/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 正常下单（验证全链路）
POST {{base}}/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "李四",
  "telephone": "13912345678",
  "city": "上海",
  "address": "南京路200号"
}

### 下单后购物车应为空
GET {{base}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 下单后统计应为0
GET {{base}}/cart/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

